Package model

Class Book

java.lang.Object
model.Product
model.Book
public class Book extends Product
The `Book` class represents a book product. It extends the `Product` class and adds specific properties and methods related to books. The properties of a book include its genre, review, and the number of copies sold. Books can be identified by their unique ID generated upon creation. This class provides methods to get and set the book's genre, review, copies sold amount, and ID. It also includes a method to update the copies sold amount by incrementing it by 1. The `Book` class overrides the `generateId()` and `toString()` methods from the `Product` class. Genre values: - 1: Science Fiction - 2: Fantasy - 3: Historical Novel
